'''Lot lizard''' is a [[prostitute]] at a truck stop. It is one of the lower rungs of the [[sex industry]] heirarchy. The term was popularized by the book [[Sarah (novel)|Sarah]] which is a fictional account of the life of a truck stop prostitute. Police report that lot lizards also engage in [[pickpocketing]], stealing wallets and other petty crimes.

